commit.message:
refactor: per-group MA now-playing (multi-syncgroup support)

- state.py: _ma_now_playing becomes dict[syncgroup_id -> now_playing];
  add get/set_ma_now_playing_for_group(), clear_ma_now_playing()
- ma_monitor.py: _find_active_syncgroup_queue -> _find_syncgroup_queues
  returning ALL matching queues; _poll_queues updates each group separately;
  disconnect calls clear_ma_now_playing(); send_queue_cmd accepts syncgroup_id
- routes/api.py: per-device ma_now_playing injected in get_client_status_for();
  global nowplaying removed from SSE; api_ma_queue_cmd passes syncgroup_id
- app.js: remove global _maNowPlaying; add _maProgSnapshots per device;
  populateDeviceCard reads dev.ma_now_playing; maQueueCmd/maCycleRepeat
  accept devIdx and send syncgroup_id; setInterval uses per-device snapshots

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
